                    <h3>Digital Marketing Specialist</h3>
                    <div class="position-meta">
                        <span><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i> Bangalore / Remote</span>
                        <span><i class="fas fa-briefcase"></i> Full-time</span>
                        <span><i class="fas fa-rupee-sign"></i> 6-10 LPA</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="position-desc">
                        <p>We're looking for an experienced web developer to train students in full stack web development technologies including HTML, CSS, JavaScript, React, Node.js, and MongoDB.</p>
                        <h4>Requirements:</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>3+ years of web development experience</li>
                            <li>Strong knowledge of modern JavaScript frameworks</li>
                            <li>Prior teaching/training experience preferred</li>
                            <li>Excellent communication skills</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    
                    <a href="#applyForm" class="btn btn-primary">Apply Now</a>
                </div>
                <div class="position-card">
                    <h3>Campus Ambassadors</h3>
                    <div class="position-meta">
                        <span><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i> Remote</span>
                        <span><i class="fas fa-briefcase"></i> Contract</span>
                        <span><i class="fas fa-rupee-sign"></i> Project-based</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="position-desc">
                        <p>Create engaging course content, exercises, and projects for our Data Science program covering Python, Pandas, NumPy, Matplotlib, and Machine Learning algorithms.</p>
                        <h4>Requirements:</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>Strong background in Data Science and ML</li>
                            <li>Experience creating educational content</li>
                            <li>Proficiency in Python data stack</li>
                            <li>Ability to explain complex concepts simply</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <br>
                    <a href="#applyForm" class="btn btn-primary">Apply Now</a>
                </div>
                <div class="position-card">
                    <h3>Marketing Managers</h3>
                    <div class="position-meta">
                        <span><i class="fas fa-map-marker-alt"></i> Bangalore</span>
                        <span><i class="fas fa-briefcase"></i> Full-time</span>
                        <span><i class="fas fa-rupee-sign"></i> 4-6 LPA</span>
                    </div>
                    <div class="position-desc">
                        <p>Connect with companies to place our students in internships and jobs. Manage placement activities and build relationships with hiring managers.</p>
                        <h4>Requirements:</h4>
                        <ul>
                            <li>2+ years in HR/recruitment/placement</li>
                            <li>Strong networking and negotiation skills</li>
                            <li>Understanding of tech roles and skills</li>
                            <li>Excellent organizational abilities</li>
                        </ul>
                    </div>
                    <br><br><br><br><br>
                    <a href="#applyForm" class="btn btn-primary">Apply Now</a>
                </div>
